1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the analysis of error performance in communication systems, which is a core topic in information theory. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses delay-limited communications, which is a key aspect of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper may be relevant to the study of bursty traffic in social networks and other information networks. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper may involve the use of algorithms and data structures to analyze the performance of communication systems. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may be relevant to the study of delay-limited communications in multimedia applications such as video streaming.
